OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing in city centre
OL,6,FA man is in critical condition after a
OL,7,Fstabbing in Bristol city centre.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Bond Street at
OL,10,Faround 11.30am on Tuesday 28 May
OL,11,Ffollowing calls from the public
OL,12,Freporting an alleged altercation
OL,13,Fbetween two men.
OL,15,FA man in his 40s was found with stab
OL,16,Fwounds near the McDonald's branch.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital by the
OL,19,Fambulance service, where he remains in
OL,20,Fa critical but stable condition.
