OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing in city centre
OL,6,FDetectives have since charged a 37-
OL,7,Fyear-old man with causing GBH with
OL,8,Fintent following the incident.
OL,10,FIan McInally, of Talbot Avenue,
OL,11,FBristol, has also been charged with
OL,12,Fpossessing a knife in a public place.
OL,14,FHe remains in police custody pending
OL,15,Fan appearance at Bristol Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt on Wednesday 29 May.
OL,18,FEnquiries into what happened are
OL,19,Funderway, with officers speaking to
OL,20,Fwitnesses and reviewing CCTV footage.
