OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing in city centre
OL,6,FInvestigating officer T/DC Andrew
OL,7,FSmetham said: "Several members of the
OL,8,Fpublic bravely intervened in this
OL,9,Fincident after seeing it take place.
OL,11,F"They disarmed a man with a knife and
OL,12,Fprevented him from leaving the area
OL,13,Fbefore officers arrived.
OL,15,F"There is never any expectation on
OL,16,Fpeople to intervene in acts of
OL,17,Fviolence and I'd like to recognise the
OL,18,Fcourage it will have taken those who
OL,19,Fput themselves in harm's way.
