OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing in city centre
OL,6,F"Another member of the public also
OL,7,Fcame to the aid of the injured man,
OL,8,Fgiving him first aid, and they too
OL,9,Fdeserve praise.
OL,11,F"While we don't believe there is any
OL,12,Fongoing risk to the public,
OL,13,Fneighbourhood officers will remain in
OL,14,Fthe area and will continue to carry
OL,15,Fout patrols in the city centre to
OL,16,Fprovide reassurance."
OL,18,FAnyone who witnessed the incident is
OL,19,Fasked to phone 101 and provide the
OL,20,Fcall handler with the reference
OL,21,F5224136363.
